metadata.name: Mercury is my birthstone.
metadata.description:
This is the first NFT by Galen Oakes. This collection was created 6 years ago and has never been seen before today. Creative Direction was conceptualized by Kelsea Rae (@fatal.attraction). Model is @sky_sky_

Collector will receive:
Signed 1/1 print
30 minute video call once a month for three months (creative advice, photography tutorial, entrepreneurship, etc)

*If collectors are in LA they can opt to get a photo shoot instead of creative consulting.

All collectors will be whitelisted for 50% of all future drops.
